# Saker Web Workspace — Environment Variables
#
# This is a static-export Next.js app served by the embedded Go server.
# No NEXT_PUBLIC_ variables are needed for the default setup.
#
# When running the frontend dev server separately (make web-dev),
# it connects to the Go backend at the URL below.

# Backend API base URL (used only in dev mode, not in production static export)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:10112